The documentes in the Broomie packages is below:

  - README    : thie file
  - COPYING   : license
  - ChangeLog : history of enhancement
  - NEWS      : information of modification
  - AUTHORS   : authors of Broomie
  - INSTALL   : how to install

Contents of the directory tree is below.

  ./src/   : sources of Broomie
  ./tests/ : test script and test data

The detailed document is below:

  http://code.google.com/p/broomie/w/list

For installation see INSTALL


MEMO
$ autoreconf --install
# aclocal; autoheader; automake -a -c; autoconf